---
title: NovaPay 8-Stage Regulated CI/CD Pipeline
---
flowchart LR
    dev["Developer / PR<br/>short-lived branch"]
    source["1. Source control<br/>Signed commits + branch protection"]
    build["2. Build + unit tests<br/>Docker build, 80% line / 70% branch"]
    sast["3. SAST<br/>SonarQube/Semgrep: 0 Critical, ≤2 High"]
    scan["4. Dependency + container scan<br/>Trivy/Grype, SBOM, licence check"]
    test["5. Integration + contract tests<br/>Pact + ephemeral namespace"]
    dast["6. DAST<br/>OWASP ZAP active/authenticated"]
    policy["7. Policy + compliance gates<br/>OPA/Kyverno, RBI, PCI-DSS, SoD"]
    deploy["8. Deployment + verification<br/>Blue-green / canary + smoke tests"]
    prod["Production verified<br/>Evidence pack + DORA event"]
    fail["Failure path<br/>Block, auto-ticket, remediation, exception workflow"]
    dev --> source
    source --> build
    build --> sast
    sast --> scan
    scan --> test
    test --> dast
    dast --> policy
    policy --> deploy
    deploy --> prod
    build -->|on gate failure| fail
    sast -->|on finding| fail
    scan -->|on CVE/licence| fail
    policy -->|on policy reject| fail
    deploy -->|on verification fail| fail
